. (2004)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9D4B0A3230FFDA8763F9D4291EF9EA" author="Pinheiro, P. S. &amp; Geise, L." box="[1053,1333,1555,1581]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="51 - 59" refId="ref72104" refString="Pinheiro, P. S. &amp; Geise, L. (2008) Non-volant mammals of Picinguaba, Ubatuba, state of Sao Paulo, southeastern Brazil. Boletim do Museu de Biologia Mello Leitao, 23, 51 - 59." type="journal article" year="2008">Pinheiro &amp; Geise (2008)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9D4B0A3230FFDA863EF9D42D09F996" author="Di-Nizo, C. B. &amp; Neves, C. L. &amp; Vilela, J. F. &amp; Silva, M. J. J." pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="11 - 30" refId="ref66320" refString="Di-Nizo, C. B., Neves, C. L., Vilela, J. F. &amp; Silva, M. J. J. (2014) New karyologycal data and cytotaxonomic considerations on small mammals from Santa Virginia (Parque Estadual da Serra do Mar, Atlantic Forest, Brazil). Comparative cytogenetics, 8 (1), 11 - 30. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / compcytogen. v 8 i 1.6430" type="journal article" year="2014">
Di-Nizo 
