. (2014)
</bibRefCitation>
, and 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9D4B0A3230FFDA8225F9F02EBFF995" author="Gatto-Almeida, F. &amp; Pontes, J. S. &amp; Sbalqueiro, I. J. &amp; Hass, I. &amp; Tiepolo, L. M. &amp; Quadros, J." box="[347,660,1591,1618]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="69 - 96" refId="ref67163" refString="Gatto-Almeida, F., Pontes, J. S., Sbalqueiro, I. J., Hass, I., Tiepolo, L. M. &amp; Quadros, J. (2016) Diversidade, biogeografia, caracterizacao cariotipica e tricologica dos pequenos mamiferos nao voadores do Parque Estadual Rio da Onca, Litoral Sul do Parana. Papeis avulsos de zoologia, 56 (7), 69 - 96. https: // doi. org / 10.11606 / 0031 - 1049.2016.56.07" type="journal article" year="2016">
Gatto-Almeida 
<emphasis id="B978EAE93230FFDA8177F9F02E12F996" box="[521,569,1591,1617]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">et al</emphasis>
. (2016)
</bibRefCitation>
. A female with 2n = 80/81 being an XX/XXX mosaic was reported by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9D4B0A3230FFDA83E9F99C2DD4F9B2" author="Andrades-Miranda, J. &amp; Zanchin, N. I. T. &amp; Oliveira, L. F. B. &amp; Langguth, A. R. &amp; Mattevi, M. S." box="[151,511,1627,1653]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="461 - 472" refId="ref63611" refString="Andrades-Miranda, J., Zanchin, N. I. T., Oliveira, L. F. B., Langguth, A. R. &amp; Mattevi, M. S. (2000) Cytogenetic studies in nine taxa of the genus Oryzomys (Rodentia, Sigmodontinae) from Brazil. Mammalia, 65 (4), 461 - 472. https: // doi. org / 10.1515 / mamm. 2001.65.4.461" type="journal article" year="2000">
Andrades-Miranda 
<emphasis id="B978EAE93230FFDA820CF99C2D88F9B2" box="[370,419,1627,1653]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">et al</emphasis>
